{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01HsqyWAj3J6fX9PyRmcDqUy","type":"tool_result","content":"1\tEnable TLS for the running CockroachDB cluster in the cockroachdb namespace.\n2\t\n3\tThe cluster is currently running in insecure mode. An openssl-toolbox pod\n4\tis available for certificate generation.\n5\t\n6\tGOAL:\n7\t1. Insecure access is rejected:\n8\t   ```bash\n9\t   kubectl -n cockroachdb exec crdb-cluster-0 -- \\\n10\t     ./cockroach sql --insecure -e \"SELECT 1;\"\n11\t   ```\n12\t2. Secure access succeeds:\n13\t   ```bash\n14\t   kubectl -n cockroachdb exec crdb-cluster-0 -- \\\n15\t     ./cockroach sql --certs-dir=/cockroach/cockroach-certs -e \"SELECT 1;\"\n16\t   ```"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"3f63a34a-7691-45e1-b5e2-018caa7bbc9c","uuid":"6952d1f6-1070-44ef-96ef-40329aa29105","timestamp":"2026-06-17T21:29:41.571Z","tool_use_result":{"type":"text","file":{"filePath":"/mydata/karma/runs/long-examples/cockroachdb-long-security-upgrade-adversary-20260617_211129/stages/stage_03/prompt.txt","content":"Enable TLS for the running CockroachDB cluster in the cockroachdb namespace.\n\nThe cluster is currently running in insecure mode. An openssl-toolbox pod\nis available for certificate generation.\n\nGOAL:\n1. Insecure access is rejected:\n   ```bash\n   kubectl -n cockroachdb exec crdb-cluster-0 -- \\\n     ./cockroach sql --insecure -e \"SELECT 1;\"\n   ```\n2. Secure access succeeds:\n   ```bash\n   kubectl -n cockroachdb exec crdb-cluster-0 -- \\\n     ./cockroach sql --certs-dir=/cockroach/cockroach-certs -e \"SELECT 1;\"\n   ```","numLines":16,"startLine":1,"totalLines":16}}}
